| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3277 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 87ca7e0e-e01a-501b-944a-5dd8e06c6d0a"
